{"config":{"lang":["en"],"min_search_length":3,"prebuild_index":true,"separator":"[\\s\\-\\.]+"},"docs":[{"location":"","text":"Welcome to Beike' blog. \u00b6 \u6b22\u8fce\u6765\u5230\u6211\u7684\u4e2a\u4eba\u535a\u5ba2. \u672c\u535a\u5ba2\u76ee\u524d\u53ea\u652f\u6301\u82f1\u6587\u641c\u7d22. \u672c\u535a\u5ba2\u4ec0\u4e48\u90fd\u6ca1\u6709.","title":"Welcome to Beike' blog."},{"location":"#welcome-to-beike-blog","text":"\u6b22\u8fce\u6765\u5230\u6211\u7684\u4e2a\u4eba\u535a\u5ba2. \u672c\u535a\u5ba2\u76ee\u524d\u53ea\u652f\u6301\u82f1\u6587\u641c\u7d22. \u672c\u535a\u5ba2\u4ec0\u4e48\u90fd\u6ca1\u6709.","title":"Welcome to Beike' blog."},{"location":"help/","text":"\u914d\u7f6e\u6587\u4ef6 \u00b6 WSL2-Ubuntu basic \u00b6 1 2 3 4 5 6 sudo apt update sudo apt upgrade sudo apt install zsh python3-pip lua5.1 luajit curl libffi-dev libffi7 libgmp-dev libgmp10 libncurses-dev libncurses5 libtinfo5 chsh -s /usr/bin/zsh zsh # \u90090 \u6dfb\u52a0 source ~/dotfiles/init/zsh/init.zsh \u5230 .zshrc ppa \u00b6 1 2 3 sudo add-apt-repository ppa:neovim-ppa/unstable sudo add-apt-repository ppa:git-core/ppa sudo apt update zsh \u00b6 1 2 3 sh -c \" $( curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/zdharma/zinit/master/doc/install.sh ) \" # \u5b89\u88c5 zinit # \u9009 n, \u7136\u540e\u6211\u624b\u52a8\u914d\u7f6e git \u00b6 1 git config --global init.defaultBranch main neovim \u00b6 1 2 3 mk .config && cd .config mk nvim && cd nvim vim init.vim \u5728 ~/.config/nvim/init.vim \u4e2d\u6dfb\u52a0 source ~/dotfiles/init/nvim/init.vim \u68c0\u67e5 :echo has(\"python3\") \u5982\u679c\u8fd4\u56de 1 , \u4e0d\u7528\u5904\u7406, \u5426\u5219 pip3 install --user pynvim \u7f51\u7edc\u95ee\u9898 \u00b6 \u6b64\u65b9\u6848\u9488\u5bf9\u4e8e\u4f7f\u7528 WSL2 \u7684\u7528\u6237 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8 sudo vim /etc/wsl.conf #\u8bbe\u7f6e\u5982\u4e0b # \u7136\u540e\u5173\u95ed WSL2 #\u5728windows\u4e2d\u4f7f\u7528 wsl --shutdown # \u7136\u540e\u91cd\u5f00WSL sudo rm /etc/resolv.conf sudo vim /etc/resolv.conf # \u6dfb\u52a0\u5982\u4e0b\u5185\u5bb9 wsl.conf 1 2 [network] generateResolvConf = false resolv.conf 1 2 3 nameserver 8.8.8.8 # \u6216\u8005\u5176\u4ed6, \u6211\u8fd9\u91cc 8.8.8.8 \u6548\u679c\u6bd4\u8f83\u597d # nameserver1.1.1.1","title":"Help"},{"location":"help/#_1","text":"WSL2-Ubuntu","title":"\u914d\u7f6e\u6587\u4ef6"},{"location":"help/#basic","text":"1 2 3 4 5 6 sudo apt update sudo apt upgrade sudo apt install zsh python3-pip lua5.1 luajit curl libffi-dev libffi7 libgmp-dev libgmp10 libncurses-dev libncurses5 libtinfo5 chsh -s /usr/bin/zsh zsh # \u90090 \u6dfb\u52a0 source ~/dotfiles/init/zsh/init.zsh \u5230 .zshrc","title":"basic"},{"location":"help/#ppa","text":"1 2 3 sudo add-apt-repository ppa:neovim-ppa/unstable sudo add-apt-repository ppa:git-core/ppa sudo apt update","title":"ppa"},{"location":"help/#zsh","text":"1 2 3 sh -c \" $( curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/zdharma/zinit/master/doc/install.sh ) \" # \u5b89\u88c5 zinit # \u9009 n, \u7136\u540e\u6211\u624b\u52a8\u914d\u7f6e","title":"zsh"},{"location":"help/#git","text":"1 git config --global init.defaultBranch main","title":"git"},{"location":"help/#neovim","text":"1 2 3 mk .config && cd .config mk nvim && cd nvim vim init.vim \u5728 ~/.config/nvim/init.vim \u4e2d\u6dfb\u52a0 source ~/dotfiles/init/nvim/init.vim \u68c0\u67e5 :echo has(\"python3\") \u5982\u679c\u8fd4\u56de 1 , \u4e0d\u7528\u5904\u7406, \u5426\u5219 pip3 install --user pynvim","title":"neovim"},{"location":"help/#_2","text":"\u6b64\u65b9\u6848\u9488\u5bf9\u4e8e\u4f7f\u7528 WSL2 \u7684\u7528\u6237 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8 sudo vim /etc/wsl.conf #\u8bbe\u7f6e\u5982\u4e0b # \u7136\u540e\u5173\u95ed WSL2 #\u5728windows\u4e2d\u4f7f\u7528 wsl --shutdown # \u7136\u540e\u91cd\u5f00WSL sudo rm /etc/resolv.conf sudo vim /etc/resolv.conf # \u6dfb\u52a0\u5982\u4e0b\u5185\u5bb9 wsl.conf 1 2 [network] generateResolvConf = false resolv.conf 1 2 3 nameserver 8.8.8.8 # \u6216\u8005\u5176\u4ed6, \u6211\u8fd9\u91cc 8.8.8.8 \u6548\u679c\u6bd4\u8